title: BRIEF-Jagged Peak Energy Says Prelim Daily Combined Volumes For Quarter Ended March 31 Were 27,311 BOE/d To 27,600 BOE/d
text:
Market News  35 AM / Updated 6 minutes ago BRIEF-Jagged Peak Energy Says Prelim Daily Combined Volumes For Quarter Ended March 31 Were 27,311 BOE/d To 27,600 BOE/d Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 23 (Reuters) - Jagged Peak Energy Inc: 
* JAGGED PEAK ENERGY INC - PRELIM DAILY COMBINED VOLUMES FOR QUARTER ENDED MARCH 31 WERE 27,311 BOE/D TO 27,600 BOE/D 
* JAGGED PEAK ENERGY SAYS REAFFIRMING PREVIOUSLY PROVIDED TOTAL CAPITAL EXPENDITURES & TOTAL NET PRODUCTION GUIDANCE FOR FULL YEAR 2018 - SEC FILING Source text: [ bit.ly/2qQuNU5 ] Further company coverage:
